B.abp=new A.fW(B.tp,"How do I create a ward?",'Open the Wards tab and tap "Create New Ward" at the bottom. Enter a name (e.g. "ICU Ward A") and an optional floor \u2014 Wardly gives you a 5-digit code to share with your team.')
B.Of=new A.aG(61656,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.aby=new A.fW(B.Of,"How do I invite my team to a ward?","On the ward card, tap the Share button \u2014 Wardly composes a message with the 5-digit code that you can drop into WhatsApp or any messaging app. Teammates open Wardly \u2192 Wards \u2192 Join Ward and enter that code.")
B.abn=new A.fW(B.n6,"What do Normal, Urgent and Low priority mean?","\u2022 Urgent \u2014 fires a high-priority push to every ward member.\n\u2022 Normal \u2014 standard push.\n\u2022 Low \u2014 silently logged for routine updates.\n\nUse Urgent sparingly so it stays attention-grabbing.")
B.abz=new A.fW(B.ed,"How do I acknowledge a note?",'Tap a note to open the thread, then tap the green check icon next to the reply box. You can also type a reply and acknowledge in one tap \u2014 your reply gets flagged "Acknowledged by you" so the whole team sees who handled it.')
B.abu=new A.fW(B.jA,"I can't find a patient \u2014 where are they?","Use the search bar at the top of the Patients tab. It searches across every ward you've joined and highlights the matching name, bed or diagnosis.")
B.On=new A.aG(62079,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.abx=new A.fW(B.On,"How do I remove a patient?",'On the patient card, tap the \u22ee menu \u2192 "Delete permanently". This erases the patient and every note tagged to them. There is no recovery, so be sure before you confirm.')
B.abA=new A.fW(B.tg,"How do I delete a ward?","Only the ward creator (the person who set it up) can delete the ward. From Wards, tap Delete on the card you own. Every patient, note and reply inside is permanently erased; the 5-digit code becomes available for reuse.")
B.abw=new A.fW(B.jC,"I'm not getting push notifications. What do I do?",'Open Profile \u2192 "Notification setup" and run through the wizard. On Samsung / Xiaomi / OnePlus devices, you also need to allow autostart and disable battery optimisation for Wardly \u2014 those OEMs aggressively kill background apps.')
B.abv=new A.fW(B.n4,"Who can see my notes?","Only members of the same ward. If a teammate hasn't joined the ward via the 5-digit code, they cannot see anything inside \u2014 enforced at the database level by Firestore security rules.")
B.ti=new A.aG(58132,"MaterialIcons",!1)
B.abr=new A.fW(B.ti,"Where is patient history stored?",'Every note is filed against the patient automatically. Open the patient \u2192 "Notes" tab to see the full timeline. Notes survive as long as the patient and ward exist.')
B.abm=new A.fW(B.th,"Can I make the text larger?","Yes. Profile \u2192 Preferences \u2192 Text size. Slide up to 150% \u2014 every screen rescales automatically.")
B.abo=new A.fW(B.tq,"Is there a dark mode?","Yes. Profile \u2192 Preferences \u2192 Dark mode. Tuned for fluorescent ward lighting and remembered across sessions.")
B.abq=new A.fW(B.tk,"How do I sign out?",'Profile \u2192 Danger zone \u2192 Sign out. You\'ll need to sign in again next time. To wipe your account entirely, use "Delete account" in the same section.')
B.abs=new A.fW(B.to,"I found a bug. How do I report it?",'Profile \u2192 Feedback & support \u2192 "Report a bug". The pre-filled email already includes your app version, platform and account so we can investigate without going back-and-forth.')
B.abt=new A.fW(B.n3,"Where do I send feature ideas?",'Profile \u2192 Feedback & support \u2192 "Suggest a feature". Every email is read \u2014 small, considered ideas get built fastest.')
